12\n| ''[[The Simpsons: Tapped Out]]''\n| Various\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Lego Dimensions]]''\n| [[Chief Wiggum]]\n|}\n\n===Documentary===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[The Aristocrats (film)|The Aristocrats]]''\n| Himself\n|\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Chicago 10 (film)|Chicago 10]]''\n| [[Abbie Hoffman]], [[Allen Ginsberg]], Various\n| Voices\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''Under the Boardwalk: The Monopoly Story''\n| Himself\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[I Know That Voice]]''\n| Himself\n|\n|}\n\n===Theme parks===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[The Simpsons Ride]]''\n| Various\n|}\n\n===Theater===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''[[Sexual Perversity in Chicago]]''\n| Bernard\n|-\n| 2004\u20132005\n| ''[[Spamalot]]''\n| Sir [[Lancelot]], French Taunter, Tim the Enchanter, Knight who says Ni\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[The Farnsworth Invention]]''\n| [[David Sarnoff]]\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''Dry Powder''\n| Rick\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Work\n! Result\n! Ref\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| 1997\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Screen Actors Guild Award]]\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Supporting Role|Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Supporting Role]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| ''The Birdcage''\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref name=birdsag>{{cite web |url=http://www.sagawards.org/awards/nominees-and-recipients/3rd-annual-screen-actors-guild-awards#nominee-1436 |title=The 3rd Annual Screen Actors Guild Awards |publisher=Screen Actors Guild Awards |accessdate=2013-03-18}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture|Outstanding Performance by a Cast]]\n| {{won}}\n| <ref name=birdsag/>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"| 1998\n| [[Annie Award]]\n| [[Annie Award for Voice Acting in a Feature Production|Outstanding Individual Achievement for Voice Act