prising (2001 film)|Uprising]]''\n| [[Mordechaj Anielewicz]]\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2002\n| ''[[Imagine That (TV series)|Imagine That]]''\n| John Miller\n| 5 episodes<br>Also executive producer\n|-\n| 2004\u20132006\n| ''[[Huff (TV series)|Huff]]''\n| Dr. Craig \"Huff\" Huffstodt\n| 25 episodes<br>Also executive producer\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2011\n| ''[[The Cleveland Show]]''\n| [[Comic Book Guy]] \n| Voice<br/>Episode: \"Hot Cocoa Bang Bang\"\n|-\n| ''[[Free Agents (U.S. TV series)|Free Agents]]''\n| Alex Taylor\n| 8 episodes\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Stand Up to Cancer]]''\n| Moe Szyslak, Apu, Rafael \n| Voices<br/>Television special\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2013\n| ''[[The Smurfs: The Legend of Smurfy Hollow]]''\n| Gargamel \n| Voice<br/>Television short\n|-\n| ''Timms Valley''\n| Chaz Babcock \n| Voice<br/>Pilot\n|-\n| 2013\u20132015\n| ''[[Family Guy]]''\n|  Various\n| Voices<br/>3 episodes\n|-\n| 2014\u20132016\n| ''[[Ray Donovan]]''\n| Ed Cochran\n| 11 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2016\n| ''[[Bordertown (2016 animated TV series)|Bordertown]]''\n| Bud Buckwald \n| Voice<br/>13 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Mack & Moxy]]''\n| Shelfish Sheldon \n| Voice<br/>12 episodes\n|-\n| 2017\u2013present\n| ''[[Brockmire]]''\n| Jim Brockmire\n| 24 episodes<br>Also executive producer\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[The Wizard of Lies]]''\n| [[Frank DiPascali]]\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Family Guy]]''\n| Police Super Intendant Chalmers\n| \"Shanksgiving\"\n|}\n\n===Video games===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n|-\n| 1996\n| ''[[The Simpsons Cartoon Studio]]''\n| Various\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1997\n| ''[[Anastasia: Adventures with Pooka and Bartok]]''\n| Bartok\n|-\n| ''[[The Simpsons: Virtual Springfield]]''\n| rowspan=\"5\" | Various\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2001\n| ''[[The Simpsons Wrestling]]''\n|-\n| ''[[The Simpsons Road Rage]]''\n|-\n| 2002\n| ''[[The Simpsons Skateboarding]]''\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''[[The Simpsons: Hit & Run]]''\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''Friends: T